race.comment: This is tricky. PICUPSTIXX (12) has turned the form around this preparation and second up led and just missed this track/distance. May take a sit today but he'll be fitter again and this is his chance to reverse a long run of outs. THE ROOKIE (5) placed but was well beaten in the same contest. Tracked the speed and won a Ballina Maiden prior and with average she can get some of the money. CIANWOOD CITY (8) also draws awkwardly but won her Maiden here well enough to give her a hope. MINI ANGEL (3) switched from a Victorian yard and needed the first-up outing. She'd win if she found her best form.
